German Chancellor Angela Merkel on Monday expressed her &#8220;sorrow and horror&#8221; over the bomb attack in Manchester, vowing that Germany will stand by Britain in the fight against terror.&#8220;This suspected terrorist attack will only strengthen our resolve to work with our British friends against those who plan and execute such inhuman acts. I assure the people in Britain: Germany stands by your side,&#8221; she said in a statement.-AFP